---
title: Hoisin Prawn and Noodle Stir Fry with Bok Choy and Pepper
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Prawn & Noodle Stir Fry with Bok Choy in just 10 minutes for a balanced and tasty meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hoisin-prawn-and-noodle-stir-fry-4f9ecfd7-1a5a68fa.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/hoisin-prawn-and-noodle-stir-fry-5f63345304af642f75674464-07feb59a.pdf
